<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GameGuardian | Your Name Hub</title>
    <style>
        /* Official GG Color Theme */
        :root {
            --gg-blue: #2c3e50;
            --gg-green: #27ae60;
            --gg-bg: #ebedef;
            --gg-border: #d1d5da;
        }

        body { 
            background-color: var(--gg-bg); 
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
            margin: 0; padding: 0; color: #333;
        }

        /* Top Navigation Bar */
        header { 
            background-color: var(--gg-blue); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 12px 20px; 
            display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        .logo { font-size: 1.2rem; font-weight: bold; letter-spacing: 1px; }
        nav a { color: #bdc3c7; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.85rem; margin-left: 15px; }

        /* Main Content Container */
        .main-container { 
            width: 95%; max-width: 900px; 
            margin: 15px auto; 
        }

        /* The Main White Box */
        .content-box {
            background: white; 
            border-top: 4px solid #3498db; 
            padding: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        h1 { font-size: 1.3rem; margin-top: 0; color: var(--gg-blue); }
        p { line-height: 1.6; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; }

        /* The Big Green Download Button */
        .download-wrapper { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; }
        .btn-download {
            background-color: var(--gg-green); 
            color: white; 
            padding: 15px 40px; 
            border-radius: 4px; 
            text-decoration: none; 
            font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.1rem;
            display: inline-block;
            box-shadow: 0 3px 0 #1e8449;
            transition: 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-download:active { transform: translateY(2px); box-shadow: 0 1px 0 #1e8449; }

        /* Feature/Script List Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            background: #fff; 
            margin-top: 20px; 
            padding: 15px;
            border-top: 4px solid #95a5a6;
        }
        .sidebar h2 { font-size: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gg-border); padding-bottom: 10px; margin-top: 0; }
        .sidebar ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }
        .sidebar li { 
            padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #f1f1f1; 
            font-size: 0.9rem; display: flex; justify-content: space-between;
        }
        .sidebar a { color: #3498db; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }

        footer { text-align: center; padding: 30px; color: #7f8c8d; font-size: 0.8rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header>
        <div class="logo">GameGuardian</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#">Forum</a>
            <a href="#">Scripts</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <div class="main-container">
        <div class="content-box">
            <h1>Red Ash Master Hub [2026]</h1>
            <p>Welcome to the official repository for Red Ash. This tool is designed for advanced memory editing on mobile devices, specializing in bypasses for modern 64-bit games.</p>
            
            <div style="background: #fdfae3; border: 1px solid #ebe3ad; padding: 10px; font-size: 0.85rem;">
                <strong>NOTICE:</strong> Make sure you are using a Virtual Space on Honor phones to avoid visual-only errors.
            </div>

            <div class="download-wrapper">
                <a href="#" class="btn-download">Download This File</a>
                <div style="font-size: 0.75rem; color: #888; margin-top: 8px;">Version 1.0.2 (9.4 MB)</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="sidebar">
            <h2>Recent Releases</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">RED ASH .LUA</a> <span>v1.2</span></li>
                <li><a href="#">NEXUS UTILITY</a> <span>v4.0</span></li>
                <li><a href="#">FORTNITE BYPASS</a> <span>ACTIVE</span></li>
                <li><a href="#">ZOOBA SPEED FIX</a> <span>UPDATED</span></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer>
        GameGuardian is a community-driven project. <br>
        &copy; 2026 RED ASH DEVELOPMENT GROUP | KUWAIT
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
